Class OrderBy

java.lang.Object
  saadadb.query.parser.OrderBy

public final class OrderBy
extends java.lang.Object

This class parse the SaadaQL clause: ORDER BY attr [ ASC | DESC ] It stores the attribut, the option and the kind of attribute (of class or of collection)
